PrecisReappointment of JOHN WILLIAM STANTS, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canadian Transportation Accident Investigation and Safety Board to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending June 30, 1996; and designation of JOHN WILLIAM STANTS as the Chairperson of the Canadian Transportation Accident Investigation and Safety Board, effective March 29, 1995.
